snippet.title: PokerDudeOnTube
snippet.description:
MY LIFE AS POKERPLAYER, TV PRODUCER AND WHATEVER FUN COMES TO MY MIND.  PokerDudeOnTube is a part time pokerplayer, gambler and TV-producer. Vlogging and trying to learn you how to make money on poker and sharing the good time he has doing it.

MY DAILY work is running a film and TV-production company called Moonlanding. On this channel I will inform - try to entertain - and learn you to be a better at poker and gambling under responsable manners. I will also share stuff on god dam everything that I might think will entertain or inform you! (PS! The quality of the videos on this channel is not representative for my daily work. Hell! This is Youtube for GOD SAKE. Thats the beauty about it.)
